---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Legal — Solagram">
  <Header />
  <main class="prose">
    <h1>Terms &amp; Legal</h1>
    <p class="muted">Last updated: 2026-04-01</p>

    <h2>1. Non-custodial wallet</h2>
    <p>
      Solagram is a non-custodial wallet. Your private keys are generated
      and stored client-side. Solagram Labs does not hold, see, or have
      the ability to recover your keys or funds. If you lose your
      passphrase and all devices where Solagram is installed, your funds
      are unrecoverable.
    </p>

    <h2>2. No investment advice</h2>
    <p>
      Content shown in Solagram (prices, charts, token listings, swap
      quotes) is informational only and does not constitute financial,
      investment, or tax advice. You are solely responsible for your
      trading decisions.
    </p>

    <h2>3. Third-party services</h2>
    <p>
      Solagram integrates Jupiter (swap routing), Telegram (UI host),
      and Solana RPC providers. Your use of Solagram is subject to the
      terms of these services.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Open source</h2>
    <p>
      Solagram's client is open source under Apache-2.0. See
      <a href="https://github.com/solagram">the repo</a>. No part of the
      code requires trust in Solagram Labs.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Contact</h2>
    <p>Security disclosures: <a href="mailto:security@solagram.example">security@solagram.example</a>.</p>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
<style>
  .prose {
    max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-8);
    color: var(--fg-dim); font-size: var(--text-base); line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .prose h1 { color: var(--fg); font-size: var(--text-3xl); letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 0; }
  .prose h2 { color: var(--fg); font-size: var(--text-lg); margin-top: var(--space-10); }
  .prose .muted { color: var(--muted); font-size: var(--text-sm); }
</style>
